    "name": "Contract Rush DX",
    "steam_appid": 1775960,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Contract Rush DX</strong> is a hand-animated run and gun, with multiple playable characters and a focus on exploration! Complete Contracts and collect power-ups that strengthen you immensely, all culminating in massive boss fights! With inspiration from flash cartoons/games of the 2000s, the visuals are hand-animated with a sharp and bold style. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775960/extras/db78b28fd8682029ac16173657d57f39.poster.avif?t=1754003209\" width=800 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775960/extras/db78b28fd8682029ac16173657d57f39.webm?t=1754003209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775960/extras/db78b28fd8682029ac16173657d57f39.mp4?t=1754003209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775960/extras/922a5b50ea441174015f361d34e0fc67.avif?t=1754003209\" width=705 height=124 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Taking on <strong>Contracts</strong> will have you exploring large levels, all with their own set of enemies, NPCs, and secrets!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Power-ups</i> will prepare you for the Contract's boss battle at the end of the level. Power-ups can increase movement speed, spread-shot bullets, fire rate, and much more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sub-Contracts</strong> will have you taking on smaller challenge levels with a variety of objectives. Earn all 3 stars in each and get rewards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775960/extras/98f9144098d69a1368619bd7caaf8919.avif?t=1754003209\" width=705 height=124 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775960/extras/00fce000f46934856680bc880a4f4339.poster.avif?t=1754003209\" width=650 height=242 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775960/extras/00fce000f46934856680bc880a4f4339.webm?t=1754003209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775960/extras/00fce000f46934856680bc880a4f4339.mp4?t=1754003209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple playable characters</strong>, all with unique play styles. Some are focused on pure shoot'em up gameplay, others centered around melee attacks. If you're having trouble on a level, sometimes trying out a new character is the key!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775960/extras/6231df86e1caa0d2466b2b12298a04eb.poster.avif?t=1754003209\" width=690 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775960/extras/6231df86e1caa0d2466b2b12298a04eb.webm?t=1754003209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1775960/extras/6231df86e1caa0d2466b2b12298a04eb.mp4?t=1754003209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
